                     <p class="- topic/p ">Rectifier mains voltage is out of tolerance or wrong phase sequence.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">53: Charger 30° temp warning</p>
